Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you realize that I am Kira, we're getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as you all can hear... {\alpha&HFF&}Higuchi is Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as you all can hear... Higuchi is Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:12.61,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(361,370)}Guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the killing of criminals cease now, {\alpha&HFF&}there would be no doubt that Higuchi has Kira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the killing of criminals cease now, there would be no doubt that Higuchi has Kira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... {\alpha&HFF&}although I've always thought that Amane would go a long way to help Yagami Light out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... although I've always thought that Amane would go a long way to help Yagami Light out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized she'd go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that she's gone this far and stopped the killings... {\alpha&HFF&}it'll become even more difficult to witness the actual method they use to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that she's gone this far and stopped the killings... it'll become even more difficult to witness the actual method they use to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think of a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}how did you manage to get Higuchi to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, how did you manage to get Higuchi to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Oh, that guy's totally crazy about Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that guy's totally crazy about Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him that I'd marry Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he's already convinced that Misa is the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I say this now, I might end up contradicting myself later on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to deny that, no matter what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But now we know Higuchi is Kira. All we've got to do is catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But now we know Higuchi is Kira. All we've got to do is catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you might call "nice work", right, Matsuda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, as things stand, {\alpha&HFF&}we're still no closer to discovering how he kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, as things stand, we're still no closer to discovering how he kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I capture him, I want to know how he kills...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the killing of criminals cease, you won't be able to see how he kills, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}In any case, even though we're going to capture Higuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In any case, even though we're going to capture Higuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that won't be until after we've determined that the judging of criminals has ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to think about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:02:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movements of those seven can be tracked about 70% of the time, while inside the company building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about outside of the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just Watari and myself, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we were to solely focus on Higuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, I've only entered five of their houses, but {\alpha&HFF&}Midou, Namikawa and Higuchi's houses have security systems that aren't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, I've only entered five of their houses, but Midou, {\alpha&HFF&}Namikawa and Higuchi's houses have security systems that aren't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, I've only entered five of their houses, but Midou, Namikawa {\alpha&HFF&}and Higuchi's houses have security systems that aren't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, I've only entered five of their houses, but Midou, Namikawa and Higuchi's houses have security systems that aren't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, Higuchi has recently build a basement that blocks electromagnetic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It even took me a full two days to infiltrate that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we thought, Higuchi is definitely suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. {\alpha&HFF&}In that case, install bugging equipment, transmitters and cameras in Higuchi's car rather than his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. In that case, install bugging equipment, transmitters and cameras in Higuchi's car rather than his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! After going through all that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea of how hard it is to break into someone's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, do you even know how many cars Higuchi owns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine. You want me to do all of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah... if they had done that a little earlier, it would have been dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry to bring this up again, but let me ask you this directly:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... I'm sorry to bring this up again, {\alpha&HFF&}but let me ask you this directly:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... I'm sorry to bring this up again, but let me ask you this directly:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember killing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still insist on saying that?! {\alpha&HFF&}I am not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still insist on saying that?! I am not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to te--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Misa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything because I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}I need you to consider these assumptions and analyze it earnestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I need you to consider these assumptions and analyze it earnestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your answer may be the first step in capturing Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's powers were then transferred to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Yagami Light has absolutely no memory of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the premise behind this analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to think on that basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's powers were then transferred to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this transfer done by Yagami Light's own will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was there someone else behind Yagami Light, who bestowed Kira's power, and transferred that power from Yagami Light to another?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those presumptions... {\alpha&HFF&}it'd have been by Yagami Light's own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those presumptions... it'd have been by Yagami Light's own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a human behind the scenes who could bestow and transfer that power... and they didn't want their methods discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little suspicious that they hadn't transferred until right at the very last moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we accept the existence of something that could look down on us from heaven, {\alpha&HFF&}there would be no way to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we accept the existence of something that could look down on us from heaven, there would be no way to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would either have died a long time ago, {\alpha&HFF&}or I'd be spending eternity being toyed with in the palm of their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would either have died a long time ago, or I'd be spending eternity being toyed with in the palm of their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that something like that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Yagami Light was Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the current Kira can use that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}thanks to that, I'm feeling 99% better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun... thanks to that, I'm feeling 99% better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll create a situation where Higuchi will not pass the power on to anyone else... {\alpha&HFF&}and let him show us how he kills people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll create a situation where Higuchi will not pass the power on to anyone else... and let him show us how he kills people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use Sakura TV to trap Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Dokkiri TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.96,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkiri TV is the Japanese version of Candid Camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll utilize the "Kira Special" that Demegawa continues to broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll arrange a three-hour show, and at the beginning of it, we'll announce that "We'll reveal Kira's identity by the end of this show!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to believe that? After all, it's on Sakura TV, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Higuchi might not even watch that program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we've got to do is contact Namikawa and ask him to call Higuchi and say: "There's trouble brewing, turn on the TV".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Higuchi sees someone who may know his secret, he'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You're planning to use Aiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to reveal that in reality he was a spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're totally wrong. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm not planning to use Aiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're totally wrong. I'm not planning to use Aiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person Higuchi sees on TV needs to be someone that he thinks he'll be able to kill, otherwise there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be blunt, it has to be someone whose name he thinks he could quickly and easily find if he tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even such a person around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be Matsuda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi believes that you were trying to eavesdrop on their meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if the supposedly dead manager begins to threaten to expose everything, he'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get Sakura TV to prepare a screen and a microphone the way they usually do with witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the silhouette and from what's being said, Higuchi should be able to work out that it's "Manager Matsui".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, we'll have the station "slip up" and momentarily reveal the face of the person behind the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll announce that by the end of the show, he'll reveal the full identity of "H", better known as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.68,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's identity will be announced at the end of this show!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Placed in that situation, all Higuchi will be concerned about, is how fast he'll be able to find out the manager's real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can predict Higuchi's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we'll be able to confirm exactly how he's been killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this plan has a flaw, it's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Higuchi is similar to the second Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and can kill someone solely by knowing their face...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Higuchi is similar to the second Kira, and can kill someone solely by knowing their face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But given that Matsuda-san is still alive, {\alpha&HFF&}and that Higuchi wants Misa, I'd say it was unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But given that Matsuda-san is still alive, and that Higuchi wants Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd say it was unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But given that Matsuda-san is still alive, and that Higuchi wants Misa, I'd say it was unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only be using this plan if criminals stop dying though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to give it two to three days to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make your own decision on whether or not to go ahead with it during this time, Matsuda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me to do it.
Comment: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the deal with this secret meeting then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa, {\alpha&HFF&}who do you think is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa, who do you think is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could even be you, Shimura, or you, Midou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came crying to me about how he could no longer go along with Kira's evil ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimura, {\alpha&HFF&}if Midou was Kira, you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimura, if Midou was Kira, you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you and Midou would have had successful lives regardless of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you would do something so stupid as to call an eight-person meeting to discuss murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I am able to figure out that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason everyone's going along with this is because they're all scared of being killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we continue this way, we'll be caught sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, in fact, unless that happens, it'll never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Shimura, let me ask you the same question. Who do you think is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi or Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi merely acts as a foil for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's necessary that Kira has someone who's not as smart as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like everyone has already figured this out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, It's likely that it's Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. {\alpha&HFF&}Higuchi is the one who desires money and promotion the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Higuchi is the one who desires money and promotion the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always talking about how he doesn't care for promotion, {\alpha&HFF&}but conversely this just shows how hung up he really is about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always talking about how he doesn't care for promotion, but conversely this just shows how hung up he really is about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He berates people, but doesn't know how to manage them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as a result he has been demoted from Director of Development to merely the Head of a Development lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one who you've asked to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We asked Ooi, {\alpha&HFF&}but he said that we're free to have our pathetic little meeting without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We asked Ooi, but he said that we're free to have our pathetic little meeting without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Typical of Ooi, always brash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Kida had to organize Coil's commission, plus the finances for it, {\alpha&HFF&}he's not Kira either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Kida had to organize Coil's commission, plus the finances for it, he's not Kira either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa, {\alpha&HFF&}after Hatori died, you received a phone call during the next meeting... who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa, after Hatori died, {\alpha&HFF&}you received a phone call during the next meeting... who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa, after Hatori died, you received a phone call during the next meeting... {\alpha&HFF&}who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa, after Hatori died, you received a phone call during the next meeting... who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimura, you're really shrewd, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira must have chosen you for your prudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. {\alpha&HFF&}Namikawa-san, are you alone right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. Namikawa-san, are you alone right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please act naturally like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, I'm with some people who've realized that the call I received from you during that meeting was odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's on the phone, Namikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I've got both Midou and Shimura with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unlikely that either of them is Kira, and both are annoyed with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, they're both happy to sit on the sidelines and watch this thing between L and Kira unfold, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we'll capture Kira, but we'll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the end for Higuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even L can be tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your response, I'm now 100% sure that it's Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa's pretty good! {\alpha&HFF&}Looking at his face, Misa thought he might be smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa's pretty good! Looking at his face, Misa thought he might be smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was a mistake on Yagami-kun's part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we'll be using the "Kira Special" shown on Sakura TV at 7pm to force Higuchi's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to contact Higuchi a few minutes after the program has started, and tell him to watch the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that the remaining six of you won't be adversely affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kida, Takahashi or Ooi attempt anything... {\alpha&HFF&}I need you to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kida, Takahashi or Ooi attempt anything... I need you to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it really is Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably be caught tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three days since I stopped judging criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I marry the second Kira, Amane, I'll have the Shinigami's Eyes, and I'll be able to control Yotsuba completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, this looks bad. Turn on Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying one of them is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and I've got plenty of proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bound to be fake. After all, this is Sakura TV we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the beginning of the program he stated; "I overheard a meeting between eight people".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who knows about the meetings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?! {\alpha&HFF&}Has someone betrayed us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?! Has someone betrayed us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then one of them was killed, so now there's only seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was Mr. "H".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"H"? {\alpha&HFF&}Hatori...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"H"? Hatori...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing this much, {\alpha&HFF&}he's either one of the other six... or Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing this much, he's either one of the other six... {\alpha&HFF&}or Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing this much, he's either one of the other six... or Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. "H" was killed because he wanted out of those meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none of them would gain a thing from doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, there shouldn't be anyone else who'd know about these meetings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be Misa's manager, I think his name was Matsui. Why the hell is he still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gambled on faking a fall from a high rise apartment, because he thought he was going to be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and escaped by landing on the veranda on the floor below, or so he said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, afterwards I wrote the name on his business card into the Death Note, just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he was in the business previously, and kept his stage name when he became a manager... or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, he says that he's been investigating Yotsuba and knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the process of contacting everyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll hang up for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the accident just now, {\alpha&HFF&}are you alright? Would you like to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the accident just now, are you alright? {\alpha&HFF&}Would you like to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the accident just now, are you alright? Would you like to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I knew that I'd be letting myself in for trouble from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I die, I'll try my best until the end - in the name of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, nice... as long as you ensure you don't make the announcement until the end of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no choice but to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Kira, Misa, will know his name as well as his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken me a while to come to this decision and make this announcement, but ever since I found out the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt that as a human being, I must persevere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... I could be exposed at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:44.17,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,That announcement isn't far off now. Stay tuned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.64,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Cosme Misa. Brilliant gloss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:54.23,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel's sparkle. Misa's Cashmere Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midou? It's me. Sakura TV is causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is in the House of Councilors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him to put pressure on the Ministry of Public Affairs and put a stop to this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching it too, and it would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is going to believe this, and doing that will just make it look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His face was on TV, {\alpha&HFF&}so we were able to identify him as Matsui Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His face was on TV, so we were able to identify him as Matsui Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namikawa contacted everyone and told them to watch the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since one of us seven is Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}Matsui Tarou will soon be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since one of us seven is Kira, Matsui Tarou will soon be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! As Kira, I'm the only one who's realized that "Matsui Tarou" is a fake name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell them that, they'll know I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:47.06,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Soon Kira's identity will become clear! Stay tuned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're right. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}Higuchi is calling Mogi-san, who's outside Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, Higuchi is calling Mogi-san, who's outside Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, here it comes. Just as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moji! Where's Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Higuchi-sama, thank you so much for doing business with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is currently having one of her rare days off, so she has gone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be back tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you where she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but she said it was private and left without telling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry. I'll be able to contact her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I know his face. If only I knew his name, I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her former manager, was he in show business?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Matsui Tarou", remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I replaced him, so I can't really tell you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For such inquiries, you should try calling the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! But they're all presently in Okinawa. Maybe you could try the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going so precisely as planned, it's almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not be scared. Just sit back and enjoy this, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll relay the call between Higuchi and the President of Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Higuchi of the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy who used to work for you, Matsui Tarou, was that his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting more and more direct. Higuchi is such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:04.78,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yes, he was using a stage name when he was a manager, Higuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows that he's getting desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's Yamada... {\alpha&HFF&}no, wait! It's Yamashita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's Yamada... no, wait! It's Yamashita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for his first name... {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for his first name... I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me! You should at least know the names of the people you employ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's no need for that kind of talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to the office it should be in the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break, we're on the first staff trip we've had in two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you insist, I'll give you the combination code to access the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you go and check it out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The records are kept in the bottom drawer of the far left hand side desk as you enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ordered alphabetically. I think it should be Yamashita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're planning on announcing it at the end of the program, I've still got two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll make a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi's status confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, everything has gone exactly as we predicted.
